kid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif faced Italy's Angela Carini in the women's 145lb [66kg] class.\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 328, \"end\": 333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9280435235299876, \"rank\": 0.05295860909156207, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 336, \"end\": 349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The match ended abruptly when Khelif landed a powerful right-hand punch to Carini's face, prompting the Italian fighter to signal for a time-out.\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.999772517982016, \"rank\": 0.00022753377792835068, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 489, \"end\": 496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9791547386494223, \"rank\": 0.010564467410605452, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her coach tried to adjust her headgear, which had slipped due to the impact.\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Although she briefly continued, Carinieventually ended the fight with 2:14 remainingin the first round, citing severe pain in her nose and concerns for her health.\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The victorygarnered significant backlash, especially from prominent figures in combat athletics.\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Former UFC championIsraelAdesanya criticized Khelif, stating, \\\"Men should not be boxing women.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 877, \"end\": 880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 0.999999999964075, \"rank\": 3.582977183716907e-11, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lol, he could not even finish her.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyway, People > politics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Amanda Balionis set for Rory McIlroy reunion after wife joins him at tournament  Do not miss:Tyson Fury's son makes rude gesture in family holiday picture  Do not miss:Inside Suarez's role in huge Uruguay vs Colombia brawl as footage emerges  Women'sboxing champion Claressa Shieldsechoed similar sentiments in an interview with Fox News, advocating for gender-specific competitions and suggesting that transgender athletes should have their category.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanda_Balionis\", \"score\": 0.9999989170584238, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amanda Balionis\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanda_Balionis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanda_Balionis\"}, {\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rory McIlroy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\"}, {\"begin\": 1136, \"end\": 1146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyson_Fury\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8449452247197995e-18, \"text\": \"Tyson Fury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyson_Fury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyson_Fury\"}, {\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9813312547015628, \"rank\": 0.018900858651946014, \"text\": \"Colombia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1372, \"end\": 1380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.15168723040001e-13, \"text\": \"Fox News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif has competed in women's athletics since her boxing debut in 2018.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's participation in women's boxing has been controversial for at least a year.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023, the International Boxing Association disqualified her from the Women's World Championships just hours before her gold medal match in New Delhi for failing to meet gender eligibility criteria.\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1667, \"end\": 1699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.542959063631578e-24, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1796, \"end\": 1805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9979551971066223, \"rank\": 0.00204897155639903, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite this, she was allowed to compete in the Olympics due to the International Olympic Committee's [IOC] rules and regulations.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1923, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bunce expressed concern over the impact of Khelif's backlash on boxing's future.\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it has hurt Olympic boxing at a crucial time where its future is still being discussed.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2166, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an absolute disaster,\\\" he saidon BBC radio.\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2205, \"end\": 2208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.7041717185988533, \"rank\": 0.38371056031854117, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He acknowledged the complex situation Khelif finds herself in, adding, \\\"You have to feel a little bit for Khelif.\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's stuck in the middle of something here that's absolutely devastating, and it's not over yet.\\\"\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the controversy, Khelif has received support from some corners of the boxing community.\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2525, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"UK veteran Amy Broadhurst, who has 109 professional fights and previously defeated Khelif, supported her former opponent.\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2526, \"end\": 2528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9993521894511015, \"rank\": 0.0006482005209045174, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2537, \"end\": 2551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Broadhurst\", \"score\": 0.999994937526562, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amy Broadhurst\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Broadhurst\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Broadhurst\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On X [formerly Twitter], Broadhurst wrote, \\\"Have a lot of people texting me over Imane Khelif.\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2674, \"end\": 2684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\", \"score\": 0.9999999986121111, \"rank\": 1.3877898563807507e-09, \"text\": \"Broadhurst\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q24354\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\"}, {\"begin\": 2730, \"end\": 2742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.99999964216